WEBVTT

00:03:59.181 --> 00:04:02.515
science, technology,
engineering, mathematics --

00:04:02.539 --> 00:04:03.751
is fierce.

00:04:03.775 --> 00:04:05.655
It's in all of our faces.

00:04:06.355 --> 00:04:08.029
And this is a colossal mistake.

00:04:09.707 --> 00:04:13.936
Since 2009, STEM majors
in the United States

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:16.016
have increased by 43 percent,

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:18.468
while the humanities have stayed flat.

00:04:18.492 --> 00:04:19.857
Our past president

00:04:21.047 --> 00:04:24.550
dedicated over a billion dollars
towards STEM education

00:04:24.574 --> 00:04:27.413
at the expense of other subjects,

00:04:27.437 --> 00:04:30.313
and our current president